# Octofit Tracker - Frontend Environment Variables

# GitHub Codespaces configuration
# Set this to your Codespace name to use Codespaces preview URLs
# For example, if your Codespace URL is:
#   https://xyzabc-8000.app.github.dev
# then set VITE_CODESPACE_NAME to: xyzabc
#
# Without this variable, the frontend will default to http://localhost:8000
VITE_CODESPACE_NAME=your-codespace-name

# To use this file:
# 1. Copy/rename .env.local.example to .env.local
# 2. Replace the value above with your actual Codespace name
# 3. Restart the Vite dev server (npm run dev)
